\v 11 Isithutha sikhupha umoya waso wonke\x + 12.16. 14.33.\x*, kodwa ohlakaniphileyo uyawuthiba\x + Hlab. 65.7.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Umbusi olalela amazwi amanga, zonke izinceku zakhe zikhohlakele.
\p
\v 13 Umyanga lomuntu wencindezelo bayahlangana\x + 22.2. Hlab. 85.10.\x*; iN\nd kosi\nd* ikhanyisa amehlo abo bobabili\x + Jobe 25.3. Mat. 5.45.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Inkosi eyahlulela abayanga ngothembeko\x + Hlab. 72.4.\x*, isihlalo sayo sobukhosi sizamiswa phakade\x + 29.4. 16.12.\x*.
