\v 15 Uswazi lokukhuza kunika inhlakanipho\x + 29.17. 13.24.\x*, kodwa umntwana oyekelelwayo\x + Isa. 16.2. 27.10.\x* uthelela\x + 10.5.\x* unina inhloni\x + 10.1.\x*.
